      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just \"difficult emotions\" though. it feels permanent. like every single thing i built is just dust now. if i go back, i'm just the guy who burned everything down. there's no \"finding a way forward\" when you're starting from negative millions. at this point, it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise and the embarrassment is to just... not be around to deal with it anymore. it feels like the only logical exit.",
